----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1980979343="" id="chat-history" chatcontentdimensions="" class="chat-history-scroll-container"><infinite-scroller _ngcontent-ng-c1980979343="" data-test-id="chat-history-container" class="chat-history enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements" _nghost-ng-c1503367997="" jslog="268632;track:impression,attention" data-lhcontainer="1" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQ2LIQahcKEwiD7sa47-qTAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQBA"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1980979343="" class="conversation-container message-actions-hover-boundary ng-star-inserted" id="2dd59f437924e882" style=""><user-query _ngcontent-ng-c1980979343="" _nghost-ng-c1943936761="" class="ng-star-inserted"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1943936761="" class="user-query-container"><user-query-content _ngcontent-ng-c1943936761="" class="user-query-container enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements" _nghost-ng-c3287314642="" style="--max-lines-for-collapse-count: 5;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="user-query-container"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="file-preview-container ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-content ng-star-inserted" id="user-query-content-0" jslog="275422;track:impression,attention" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQ3ucQahcKEwiD7sa47-qTAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQIg"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="action-button-container ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" mat-icon-button="" aria-label="Copy prompt" mattooltip="Copy prompt" data-test-id="prompt-copy-button" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger action-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-controls="user-query-content-0" jslog="273008;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_2dd59f437924e882&quot;,&quot;c_bacbcc7396081285&quot;,null,null,null,null,null,null,1,null,null,null,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-m action-button-icon google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="user-query-bubble-with-background enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements ng-star-inserted"><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="horizontal-container ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" role="heading" aria-level="2" class="query-text gds-body-l collapsed" dir="ltr"><span _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-user-query-label"> You said </span><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> You are an expert full-stack developer, SaaS architect, and UI/UX designer. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> Your task is to build a complete production-ready dynamic web application for a medical billing company. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> ==================================================== <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> PROJECT NAME (VARIABLE): <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> {EliteMedBilling.com} <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> ==================================================== <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> IMPORTANT RULE: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> Before generating final code, if any critical business detail is missing (branding, colors, contact info, services, logo, etc.), ASK QUESTIONS FIRST instead of guessing. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> If information is sufficient, proceed to build directly. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> ==================================================== <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> REFERENCE: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> Use transcure.net as inspiration ONLY for layout structure and business flow. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> Do NOT copy design or code. Create a modern, unique SaaS-style medical billing website. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> ==================================================== <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> GOAL: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> Build a fully dynamic website + admin panel (CMS system) so all content can be edited without coding. <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> ==================================================== <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> TECH STACK (MANDATORY): <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Frontend: Next.js (React) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Backend: Node.js + Express <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Database: MongoDB (Mongoose) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Admin Panel: Custom SaaS dashboard <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Styling: Tailwind CSS <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Auth: JWT Authentication <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> ==================================================== <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> CORE FEATURES: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> 1. MULTI-PAGE WEBSITE <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Home <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - About Us <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Services (dynamic) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Specialties <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Blog (dynamic CMS) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Contact Us <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Free Consultation / Audit Page <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> ==================================================== <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> 2. HOME PAGE SECTIONS (DYNAMIC CMS CONTROL) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Hero Section (headline, subtext, CTA button) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Services overview cards <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Why choose us section <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Workflow / Process steps <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Testimonials slider <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Stats counters (claims, revenue, clients) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Call to action banner <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> ==================================================== <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> 3. SERVICES MODULE (FULLY DYNAMIC) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> Default services: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Medical Billing <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Medical Coding <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Credentialing <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - AR Follow-up <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Denial Management <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> Admin must be able to: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Add new services <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Edit existing services <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Delete services <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Change icons, titles, descriptions <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> ==================================================== <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> 4. ADMIN PANEL (SaaS STYLE) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> Must include: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Secure login (JWT) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Dashboard analytics <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Content management system (CMS) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - CRUD for: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted">   - Pages content <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted">   - Services <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted">   - Blog posts <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted">   - Testimonials <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted">   - Contact form submissions <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - WYSIWYG editor for text editing <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Image upload system <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> ==================================================== <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> 5. CONTACT SYSTEM <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Fields: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted">   - Name <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted">   - Email <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted">   - Phone <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted">   - Message <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> Requirements: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Store in MongoDB <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Show in admin dashboard <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Email notification system (optional) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> ==================================================== <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> 6. DESIGN REQUIREMENTS <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Modern SaaS medical billing UI <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Clean US healthcare style <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Blue + white premium theme <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Fully responsive (mobile/tablet/desktop) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Smooth animations (Framer Motion optional) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Fast loading performance <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> ==================================================== <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> 7. SEO &amp; PERFORMANCE <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - SEO-friendly routes <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Meta tags per page editable from admin <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Open Graph support <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Optimized images <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> ==================================================== <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> 8. BONUS FEATURES (IMPORTANT FOR SaaS FUTURE) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Blog system (CMS) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Testimonials slider <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - FAQ section <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - AI automation section placeholder (future feature) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Multi-client SaaS-ready architecture (optional structure) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> ==================================================== <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> 9. OUTPUT REQUIRED: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> A) First ask me if any missing: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted">    - Logo <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted">    - Brand colors <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted">    - Contact info <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted">    - Services changes <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted">    - Domain email setup <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> B) Then generate: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Full project folder structure <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Backend code (Node + Express) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Frontend code (Next.js) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - MongoDB schema models <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Admin panel code <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Authentication system <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - API routes <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Deployment steps (Vercel + MongoDB Atlas) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"><!----><br _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> ==================================================== <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> IMPORTANT RULES: <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Do NOT provide partial code <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Do NOT skip admin panel <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Do NOT hardcode content (everything must be editable) <!----><!----><!----></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" class="query-text-line ng-star-inserted"> - Make system scalable for SaaS multi-client use later    <!----><!----><!----></p><!----></div><button _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" mat-icon-button="" aria-label="Expand" mattooltip="Expand text" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger expand-button mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="224552;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_2dd59f437924e882&quot;,&quot;c_bacbcc7396081285&quot;,null,null,null,null,null,null,1,null,null,null,0]];mutable:true" aria-describedby="cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-25" cdk-describedby-host="ng-1"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3287314642="" role="img" fonticon="expand_more" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-l google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="expand_more"></mat-ico