MONGODB_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=use_a_long_random_string
EMAIL_USER=contact@elitemedbilling.com
SMTP_PASS=your_smtp_password
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:5000
</code></pre><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><h3 data-path-to-node="23"><b data-path-to-node="23" data-index-in-node="0">Step 3: Vercel + Render Deployment</b></h3><ul data-path-to-node="24"><li><p data-path-to-node="24,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="24,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Backend:</b> Deploy the <code data-path-to-node="24,0,0" data-index-in-node="20">/backend</code> folder to <b data-path-to-node="24,0,0" data-index-in-node="39">Render.com</b> or <b data-path-to-node="24,0,0" data-index-in-node="53">Railway.app</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="24,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="24,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Frontend:</b> Deploy the <code data-path-to-node="24,1,0" data-index-in-node="21">/frontend</code> folder to <b data-path-to-node="24,1,0" data-index-in-node="41">Vercel</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="24,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="24,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Images:</b> Upload the logo from watermarked_img_17958641478171189224.png to the <code data-path-to-node="24,2,0" data-index-in-node="77">/public/images</code> folder.</p></li></ul><p data-path-to-node="25"><b data-path-to-node="25" data-index-in-node="0">Ready to launch?</b> I can provide the specific API route code for the Contact Form or the JWT Auth logic next if you'd like to dive deeper into a specific module!</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="response-fo