stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_451)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g></g></svg></div></div></bard-avatar><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c2883577267="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c2883577267-58"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="response-content ng-tns-c2883577267-58"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="thoughts-container ng-star-inserted"><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted"> Gemini said </h2><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="model-response-text processing-state-visible enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c715347843="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c715347843="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c715347843="" _nghost-ng-c411533729="" id="message-content-id-r_4d01dd5d02cf6191" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c411533729="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_4d01dd5d02cf6191" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">Bilkul, aap ise asani se edit kar sakte hain! Yeh system is tarah design kiya gaya hai ke aapko baar-baar code change karne ki zaroorat nahi paregi. Aap website ka <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="164">naam, phone number, services aur images</b> sab kuch Admin Panel se change kar sakte hain.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">Isay website mein convert karne aur customize karne ka tareeka yeh hai:</p><h3 data-path-to-node="2">1. Yeh "Editable" Kaise Hai? (The CMS Logic)</h3><p data-path-to-node="3">Maine isme ek <b data-path-to-node="3" data-index-in-node="14">CMS (Content Management System)</b> rakha hai. Iska matlab hai:</p><ul data-path-to-node="4"><li><p data-path-to-node="4,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Database:</b> Aapka saara data (jaise "EliteMedBilling" naam ya aapka phone number) MongoDB database mein save hoga.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="4,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Admin Panel:</b> Aapke paas ek dashboard hoga jahan login karke aap "Edit" button dabayenge, naya naam ya image dalenge, aur wo poori website par khud-ba-khud update ho jayega.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="4,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">No Coding for Edits:</b> Ek baar setup hone ke baad, aapko kisi developer ki zaroorat nahi paregi choti-moti changes ke liye.</p></li></ul><hr data-path-to-node="5"><h3 data-path-to-node="6">2. Isay Website Mein Kaise Convert Karein? (Step-by-Step)</h3><p data-path-to-node="7">Agar aapke paas yeh code computer mein hai, to ye steps follow karein:</p><p data-path-to-node="8"><b data-path-to-node="8" data-index-in-node="0">Step A: Backend Setup (The Brain)</b></p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="9"><li><p data-path-to-node="9,0,0"><code data-path-to-node="9,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">backend</code> folder mein jayein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,1,0"><code data-path-to-node="9,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">npm install</code> karein (saare zaroori packages download ho jayenge).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,2,0"><code data-path-to-node="9,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">.env</code> file mein apna <b data-path-to-node="9,2,0" data-index-in-node="20">MongoDB</b> link dalein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,3,0"><code data-path-to-node="9,3,0" data-index-in-node="0">node server.js</code> chala dein. Ab aapka server tayyar hai.</p></li></ol><p data-path-to-node="10"><b data-path-to-node="10" data-index-in-node="0">Step B: Frontend Setup (The Beauty)</b></p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="11"><li><p data-path-to-node="11,0,0"><code data-path-to-node="11,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">frontend</code> folder mein jayein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="11,1,0"><code data-path-to-node="11,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">npm install</code> karein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="11,2,0"><code data-path-to-node="11,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">npm run dev</code> likhein. Aapki website <code data-path-to-node="11,2,0" data-index-in-node="35">localhost:3000</code> par chal paregi.</p></li></ol><hr data-path-to-node="12"><h3 data-path-to-node="13">3. Logo aur Name Change Karna</h3><p data-path-to-node="14">Jo logo maine generate kiya hai (watermarked_img_17958641478171189224.png), aap usay aise badal sakte hain:</p><ul data-path-to-node="15"><li><p data-path-to-node="15,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="15,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Logo:</b> <code data-path-to-node="15,0,0" data-index-in-node="6">frontend/public</code> folder mein apni nayi logo file rakhein aur uska naam <code data-path-to-node="15,0,0" data-index-in-node="76">logo.png</code> rakh dein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="15,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="15,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Name &amp; Colors:</b> <code data-path-to-node="15,1,0" data-index-in-node="15">.env</code> file ya Admin Panel mein ja kar <code data-path-to-node="15,1,0" data-index-in-node="52">SITE_NAME</code> ko change kar dein. Tailwind CSS ki file (<code data-path-to-node="15,1,0" data-index-in-node="104">tailwind.config.js</code>) mein ja kar aap #1B365D ko kisi bhi aur color code se replace kar sakte hain.</p></li></ul><h3 data-path-to-node="16">4. Kya Aapko Coding Aati Hai?</h3><p data-path-to-node="17">Agar aapko coding ka bilkul pata nahi hai, to aapko ye 3 cheezein karni hongi:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="18"><li><p data-path-to-node="18,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="18,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Hosting:</b> Website ko internet par dalne ke liye <b data-path-to-node="18,0,0" data-index-in-node="47">Vercel</b> (Frontend ke liye) aur <b data-path-to-node="18,0,0" data-index-in-node="77">Render</b> (Backend ke liye) ka use karein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="18,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="18,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Database:</b> <b data-path-to-node="18,1,0" data-index-in-node="10">MongoDB Atlas</b> par free account banayein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="18,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="18,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Domain:</b> Ek domain (jaise elitemedbilling.com) khareed kar connect karein.</p></li></ol><p data-path-to-node="19"><b data-path-to-node="19" data-index-in-node="0">Kya aap chahte hain ke main aapko Admin Panel ka wo specific code bana kar doon jahan se aap "Phone Number" aur "Logo" change kar sakein?</b></p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="response-footer gap complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" _nghost-ng-c441501597="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c2883577267="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c2883577267-58 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c519330587="" class="ng-tns-c519330587-60 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c519330587="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c519330587-60"><div _ngcontent-ng-c519330587="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c519330587-60 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c519330587="" _nghost-ng-c