C1.5509999990463257,-15 3.0480000972747803,-14.763999938964844 4.455999851226807,-14.326000213623047"></path></g></g><g transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,16,16)" opacity="1" style="display: none;"><g opacity="1" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_594)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4" stroke-opacity="1" stroke-width="2" d=" M-4.815000057220459,-14.208999633789062 C-3.302999973297119,-14.722000122070312 -1.684000015258789,-15 0,-15 C0,-15 0,-15 0,-15 C1.5579999685287476,-15 3.061000108718872,-14.76200008392334 4.473999977111816,-14.319999694824219"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_590)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_586)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_579)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g></g></svg></div></div></bard-avatar><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c2883577267="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c2883577267-63"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="response-content ng-tns-c2883577267-63"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="thoughts-container ng-star-inserted"><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted"> Gemini said </h2><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="model-response-text processing-state-visible enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c715347843="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c715347843="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c715347843="" _nghost-ng-c411533729="" id="message-content-id-r_56ba68cf8a49f318" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c411533729="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_56ba68cf8a49f318" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">Bilkul, aap <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="12">Cloudflare Pages</b> par direct upload kar sakte hain, lekin aapko aik baat samajhni hogi: Cloudflare Pages sirf <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="121">Frontend</b> (jo nazar aata hai) host karta hai. Aapka <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="172">Backend</b> (Database aur Admin logic) kahin aur host hoga (jaise Render ya Railway), tabhi aap "Edit" kar sakenge.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">Lekin tension na lein, main aapko sabse asaan tareeka batata hoon jis se aap baghair code likhe bad mein domain aur content change kar sakein.</p><hr data-path-to-node="2"><h3 data-path-to-node="3">1. Cloudflare Pages par Post kaise karein?</h3><p data-path-to-node="4">Aapko code ko <b data-path-to-node="4" data-index-in-node="14">GitHub</b> par upload karna hoga. Phir Cloudflare Pages us GitHub se khud hi connect ho jayega.</p><ul data-path-to-node="5"><li><p data-path-to-node="5,0,0">Jab bhi aap GitHub par file change karenge, Cloudflare par website khud hi update ho jayegi.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="5,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Domain Change:</b> Cloudflare ke dashboard mein "Custom Domains" ka option hota hai jahan aap apna <code data-path-to-node="5,1,0" data-index-in-node="95">elitemedbilling.com</code> asani se connect kar sakte hain.</p></li></ul><hr data-path-to-node="6"><h3 data-path-to-node="7">2. Isay "Editable" banane ka Secret (Easy Way)</h3><p data-path-to-node="8">Agar aap professional coding nahi jante, to main aapke liye <b data-path-to-node="8" data-index-in-node="60">Direct Frontend-to-Database</b> system set kar deta hoon. Is se aapka Admin Panel asaan ho jayega.</p><p data-path-to-node="9">Main aapko <b data-path-to-node="9" data-index-in-node="11">Backend ka wo Code</b> de raha hoon jo aapke "Name" aur "Phone" ko control karega:</p><h4 data-path-to-node="10"><b data-path-to-node="10" data-index-in-node="0">Backend Model (Settings Schema)</b></h4><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-70 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="code-block ng-tns-c3933017335-70 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_56ba68cf8a49f318&quot;,&quot;c_bacbcc7396081285&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c60e5f87186e8cff&quot;,null,null,&quot;&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahcKEwiD7sa47-qTAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQfg" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c3933017335-70 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-70">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="buttons ng-tns-c3933017335-70 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" aria-label="Download code" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Download code" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger download-button ng-tns-c3933017335-70 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered=""><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" role="img" fonticon="download" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="download"></mat-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" aria-label="Copy code" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copy code" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c3933017335-70 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_56ba68cf8a49f318&quot;,&quot;c_bacbcc7396081285&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c60e5f87186e8cff&quot;,null,null,&quot;&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c3933017335-70"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c3933017335-70"><!----><pre _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-70"><code _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c3933017335-70"><span class="hljs-comment">// Ye file control karegi aapki website ki main info</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> SettingsSchema = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> mongoose.Schema({
  <span class="hljs-attr">siteName</span>: { <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">default</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"EliteMedBilling"</span> },
  <span class="hljs-attr">phoneNumber</span>: { <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">default</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"+1-XXX-XXX-XXXX"</span> },
  <span class="hljs-attr">email</span>: { <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">default</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"info@elitemedbilling.com"</span> },
  <span class="hljs-attr">address</span>: { <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span> },
  <span class="hljs-attr">logoUrl</span>: { <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span> } <span class="hljs-comment">// Yahan aap watermarked_img_17958641478171189224.png ka link dalenge</span>
});
</code></pre><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><hr data-path-to-node="12"><h3 data-path-to-node="13">3. Aapko kya karna hai? (Action Plan)</h3><p data-path-to-node="14">Aapko sirf ye steps follow karne hain:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="15"><li><p data-path-to-node="15,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="15,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">GitHub Account Banayein:</b> Apni files wahan upload karein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="15,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="15,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Cloudflare Pages Connect karein:</b> Cloudflare dashboard mein "Create a project" -&gt; "Connect to Git" karein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="15,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="15,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Environment Variables (Key Step):</b> Cloudflare ki settings mein ja kar aapko <code data-path-to-node="15,2,0" data-index-in-node="75">DATABASE_URL</code> dalni hogi.</p></li></ol><h3 data-path-to-node="16"><b data-path-to-node="16" data-index-in-node="0">Main aapko poora code (Zip ki tarah) structure bana kar deta hoon?</b></h3><p data-path-to-node="17">Main aapko aik aisi <b data-path-to-node="17" data-index-in-node="20">"Admin Settings"</b> screen bana kar de deta hoon jahan se aap:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="18"><li><p data-path-to-node="18,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="18,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Name</b> change kar sakein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="18,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="18,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Phone Number</b> badal sakein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="18,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="18,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Services</b> ki list update kar sakein.</p></li></ol><p data-path-to-node="19"><b data-path-to-node="19" data-index-in-node="0">Kya main Admin Screen ka simple code generate karoon jo aap Cloudflare par test kar sakein?</b></p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="response-footer gap complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" _nghost-ng-c441501597="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c2883577267="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c2883577267-63 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c519330587="" class="ng-tns-c519330587-66 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c519330587="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c519330587-66"><div _ngcontent-ng-c519330587="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c519330587-66 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c519330587="" _nghost-ng-c3604396107="" class="ng-tns-c519330587-66 ng-star-inserted"><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c3604396107="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Good response" aria-label="Good response" data-test-id="thumb-up-button" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger icon-button mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-pressed="false" jslog="173913;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot