</stop><stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgb(49,134,255)"></stop><stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgb(49,134,255)"></stop><stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgb(49,134,255)"></stop></lineargradient></defs><g clip-path="url(#__lottie_element_837)"><g transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,16,16)" opacity="1" style="display: block;"><g opacity="1" transform="matrix(1,0,0,1,0,0)"><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_864)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4" stroke-opacity="1" stroke-width="2" d=" M-4.383999824523926,-14.347999572753906 C-2.996999979019165,-14.772000312805176 -1.524999976158142,-15 0,-15 C0,-15 0,-15 0,-15 C1.7100000381469727,-15 3.3540000915527344,-14.713000297546387 4.886000156402588,-14.1850004196167"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_860)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_856)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_852)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_848)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_841)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g></g></svg></div></div></bard-avatar><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c2883577267="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c2883577267-78"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="response-content ng-tns-c2883577267-78"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="thoughts-container ng-star-inserted"><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted"> Gemini said </h2><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="model-response-text processing-state-visible enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c715347843="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c715347843="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c715347843="" _nghost-ng-c411533729="" id="message-content-id-r_23a57f32db4cc5a9" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c411533729="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_23a57f32db4cc5a9" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">Bilkul! Aapka concept bilkul sahi hai. Aap <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="43">Blog</b> aur <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="52">Customer Reviews</b> ko dynamic rakh sakte hain taake aap rozana ya haftawar nayi post kar sakein, jabke <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="153">Services</b> aur <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="166">Specialties</b> ko ek baar add karke wahan chhor sakte hain.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">Aapke liye main <b data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="16">Next.js (Frontend)</b> aur <b data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="39">Node.js (Backend)</b> ka aisa structure bana raha hoon jo "Editable" hoga.</p><h3 data-path-to-node="2">1. Blog &amp; Review (Dynamic - Daily Edit)</h3><p data-path-to-node="3">Iske liye main aapko ek <b data-path-to-node="3" data-index-in-node="24">Admin Panel</b> ka code dunga jahan aap:</p><ul data-path-to-node="4"><li><p data-path-to-node="4,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Create Post:</b> Title, Content (WYSIWYG editor), aur Image upload kar sakein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="4,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Manage Reviews:</b> Customers ke reviews approve ya delete kar sakein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="4,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Auto-Update:</b> Jab aap yahan save karenge, website par blog khud-ba-khud show ho jayega.</p></li></ul><h3 data-path-to-node="5">2. Specialties &amp; Physicians (Static - One-time)</h3><p data-path-to-node="6">Specialties aur Physicians ke liye hum ek <b data-path-to-node="6" data-index-in-node="42">"Admin CRUD"</b> page banayenge. Aap ise <b data-path-to-node="6" data-index-in-node="79">ek baar</b> add kar denge, lekin agar baad mein kabhi koi nayi specialty (jaise 'Radiology') add karni ho, to aap wahan ja kar <b data-path-to-node="6" data-index-in-node="202">'Add New'</b> par click karenge aur wo list mein add ho jayegi.</p><hr data-path-to-node="7"><h3 data-path-to-node="8">Folder Structure (Zip File ka Plan)</h3><p data-path-to-node="9">Jab aap ise download karenge, to folder structure aisa hoga:</p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-84 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="code-block ng-tns-c3933017335-84 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_23a57f32db4cc5a9&quot;,&quot;c_bacbcc7396081285&quot;,null,&quot;rc_2f387007ad766a7d&quot;,null,null,&quot;hi-Latn&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahgKEwiD7sa47-qTAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQmQE" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c3933017335-84 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-84">Plaintext</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="buttons ng-tns-c3933017335-84 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" aria-label="Download code" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Download code" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger download-button ng-tns-c3933017335-84 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered=""><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" role="img" fonticon="download" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="download"></mat-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" aria-label="Copy code" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copy code" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c3933017335-84 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_23a57f32db4cc5a9&quot;,&quot;c_bacbcc7396081285&quot;,null,&quot;rc_2f387007ad766a7d&quot;,null,null,&quot;hi-Latn&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c3933017335-84"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c3933017335-84"><!----><pre _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-84"><code _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c3933017335-84">/EliteMedBilling-App
├── /admin-panel        # Yahan se aap blog, review, aur specialty edit karenge
├── /client-site        # Yeh aapki main website (Cloudflare/Vercel)
├── /server-api         # Yeh database (MongoDB) se connect hoga
└── README.md           # Deployment ka asaan guide
</code></pre><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><hr data-path-to-node="11"><h3 data-path-to-node="12">🚀 Kya Aap Ready Hain?</h3><p data-path-to-node="13">Main ab aapke liye <b data-path-to-node="13" data-index-in-node="19">ek "All-in-One" package (Code)</b> taiyaar kar raha hoon jo aap Seedha <b data-path-to-node="13" data-index-in-node="86">GitHub</b> par upload karke <b data-path-to-node="13" data-index-in-node="110">Cloudflare/Vercel</b> se link kar sakte hain.</p><p data-path-to-node="14"><b data-path-to-node="14" data-index-in-node="0">Iske liye mujhe confirm kar dein:</b></p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="15"><li><p data-path-to-node="15,0,0">Kya main <b data-path-to-node="15,0,0" data-index-in-node="9">Next.js 14 (App Router)</b> use karoon? (Yeh sabse fast hai aur SEO ke liye best hai).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="15,1,0">Kya main <b data-path-to-node="15,1,0" data-index-in-node="9">Tailwind CSS</b> ka design use karoon taake aap baad mein colors asani se change kar sakein?</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="15,2,0">Kya main <b data-path-to-node="15,2,0" data-index-in-node="9">Cloudinary</b> (Free image hosting) ka logic shamil karoon taake jab aap blog post karein to images automatically upload ho jayen?</p></li></ol><p data-path-to-node="16"><b data-path-to-node="16" data-index-in-node="0">Jaise hi aap "Yes" kahenge, main aapko poora file structure provide kar dunga.</b> Aap phir use apne folder mein daal kar host kar sakenge.</p><p data-path-to-node="17"><i data-path-to-node="17" data-index-in-node="0">Note: Yeh diagram aapko samajhne mein madad karega ke aapka "Admin Panel" aur "Frontend" kaise aas-paas rahenge.</i></p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="response-footer complete gap"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" _nghost-ng-c441501597="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c2883577267="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c2883577267-78 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c519330587="" class="ng-tns-c519330587-79 hide-action-bar ng-tns-c2883577267-78 ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c519330587="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c519330587-79"><div _ngcontent-ng-c519330587="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c519330587-79 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c519330587="" _nghost-ng-c3604396107="" class="ng-tns-c519330587-79 ng-star-inserted"><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c3604396107="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Good response" aria-label="Good response" data-test-id="thumb-up-button" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger icon-button mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-pressed="false" jslog="173913;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_23a57f32db4cc5a9&quot;,&quot;c_bacbcc7396081285&quot;,null,&quot;rc_2f387007ad766a7d&quot;,null,null,&quot;hi-Lat