troke="url(#__lottie_element_925)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_921)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_914)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g></g></svg></div></div></bard-avatar><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c2883577267="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c2883577267-85"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="response-content ng-tns-c2883577267-85"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="thoughts-container ng-star-inserted"><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted"> Gemini said </h2><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="model-response-text processing-state-visible enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c715347843="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c715347843="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c715347843="" _nghost-ng-c411533729="" id="message-content-id-r_2ec1721a180d076d" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c411533729="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_2ec1721a180d076d" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">Bilkul sahi! Mainay <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="20">Transcure</b> aur <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="34">PRG (Physicians Resource Group)</b> ka audit kiya hai. Ye dono websites "Trust" aur "Authority" par base karti hain. Maine unka layout aur logic study kar liya hai aur ab main aapke liye aik aisi "Production-Ready" structure bana raha hoon jo in dono se behtar aur modern hogi.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">Main <b data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="5">Next.js 14</b>, <b data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="17">Tailwind CSS</b>, aur <b data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="35">Cloudinary</b> use kar raha hoon taake aapka system bilkul SaaS-style aur super fast ho.</p><h3 data-path-to-node="2">📁 EliteMedBilling: Project Structure (The "Zip" Plan)</h3><p data-path-to-node="3">Aapko sirf ye files apne computer mein ek folder mein rakhni hain aur GitHub par push karni hain.</p><h4 data-path-to-node="4">1. Database Model (The Core)</h4><p data-path-to-node="5">Ye models aapke blogs, reviews, aur specialties ko handle karenge.</p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-92 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="code-block ng-tns-c3933017335-92 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_2ec1721a180d076d&quot;,&quot;c_bacbcc7396081285&quot;,null,&quot;rc_d7865ed0981e3a8b&quot;,null,null,&quot;&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahgKEwiD7sa47-qTAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQpwE" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c3933017335-92 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-92">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="buttons ng-tns-c3933017335-92 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" aria-label="Download code" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Download code" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger download-button ng-tns-c3933017335-92 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered=""><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" role="img" fonticon="download" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="download"></mat-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" aria-label="Copy code" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copy code" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c3933017335-92 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_2ec1721a180d076d&quot;,&quot;c_bacbcc7396081285&quot;,null,&quot;rc_d7865ed0981e3a8b&quot;,null,null,&quot;&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c3933017335-92"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c3933017335-92"><!----><pre _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-92"><code _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c3933017335-92"><span class="hljs-comment">// models/Content.js</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> mongoose = <span class="hljs-built_in">require</span>(<span class="hljs-string">'mongoose'</span>);

<span class="hljs-comment">// Blog Post Schema</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> PostSchema = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> mongoose.Schema({
  <span class="hljs-attr">title</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>,
  <span class="hljs-attr">slug</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>,
  <span class="hljs-attr">content</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>, <span class="hljs-comment">// Full HTML from WYSIWYG</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">image</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>, <span class="hljs-comment">// Cloudinary URL</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">category</span>: { <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">default</span>: <span class="hljs-string">'Medical Billing'</span> },
  <span class="hljs-attr">createdAt</span>: { <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">Date</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">default</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">Date</span>.now }
});

<span class="hljs-comment">// Specialty Schema (Physicians, Labs, etc.)</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> SpecialtySchema = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> mongoose.Schema({
  <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>, <span class="hljs-comment">// e.g., Cardiology, Pathology</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">description</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>,
  <span class="hljs-attr">icon</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>
});

<span class="hljs-comment">// Review Schema</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> ReviewSchema = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> mongoose.Schema({
  <span class="hljs-attr">clientName</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>,
  <span class="hljs-attr">designation</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>, <span class="hljs-comment">// e.g., Dr. Smith or Clinic Manager</span>
  <span class="hljs-attr">rating</span>: { <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">Number</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">default</span>: <span class="hljs-number">5</span> },
  <span class="hljs-attr">comment</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>,
  <span class="hljs-attr">isApproved</span>: { <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">Boolean</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">default</span>: <span class="hljs-literal">false</span> } <span class="hljs-comment">// Admin can approve before showing</span>
});
</code></pre><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><h4 data-path-to-node="7">2. Admin Panel Functionality</h4><p data-path-to-node="8">Main isme aik <b data-path-to-node="8" data-index-in-node="14">"Master Dashboard"</b> shamil kar raha hoon jahan se aap ye sab kaam baghair code ke kar sakenge:</p><ul data-path-to-node="9"><li><p data-path-to-node="9,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="9,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Blog Tab:</b> "Add New Post" button, jahan aap image upload karenge aur text likhenge.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="9,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Specialties Tab:</b> Aik hi baar "Physicians", "Labs", "Anesthesia" add kar dein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="9,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Reviews Tab:</b> Jab koi customer review dega, wo yahan show hoga. Aap "Approve" dabayenge to website par live ho jayega.</p></li></ul><hr data-path-to-node="10"><h3 data-path-to-node="11">🚀 Key Design Decisions (Inspired by PRG &amp; Transcure)</h3><ul data-path-to-node="12"><li><p data-path-to-node="12,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="12,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Premium Blue Palette:</b> Humne wohi Navy Blue (#1B365D) aur Sky Blue (#0EA5E9) use kiya hai jo aapne logo (watermarked_img_17958641478171189224.png) mein pasand kiya tha.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="12,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="12,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Conversion Focus:</b> Website ke har page par "Get a Free Audit" ka button hoga (bilkul Transcure ki tarah).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="12,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="12,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Mobile Responsive:</b> Aapka Admin Panel aur Website dono mobile par perfect chalenge.</p></li></ul><hr data-path-to-node="13"><h3 data-path-to-node="14">🛠️ Next Steps: How to Host on Cloudflare</h3><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="15"><li><p data-path-to-node="15,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="15,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Code Download:</b> Main aapko poora code provide karunga.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="15,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="15,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">GitHub:</b> Aap aik naya repository banayenge aur ye files wahan upload (drag &amp; drop) kar denge.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="15,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="15,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Cloudflare Pages:</b> Cloudflare dashboard mein ja kar "New Project" -&gt; "Connect to GitHub" select karein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="15,3,0"><b data-path-to-node="15,3,0" data-index-in-node="0">Auto-Build:</b> Cloudflare khud hi aapki website "build" kar ke live kar dega.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="15,4,0"><b data-path-to-node="15,4,0" data-index-in-node="0">Domain:</b> Jab aapka domain (<code data-path-to-node="15,4,0" data-index-in-node="26">elitemedbilling.com</code>) ready ho jaye, Cloudflare mein "Custom Domain" par click karke add kar dein.</p></li></ol><p data-path-to-node="16"><b data-path-to-node="16" data-index-in-node="0">Kya main poora code (Frontend + Backend) aik hi baar generate kar doon taake aap use folder mein save kar sakein?</b> Main step-by-step code chunks mein dunga taake koi file miss na ho.</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="response-footer gap complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!-