inecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_1042)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g></g></svg></div></div></bard-avatar><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c2883577267="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c2883577267-93"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="response-content ng-tns-c2883577267-93"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="thoughts-container ng-star-inserted"><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted"> Gemini said </h2><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="model-response-text processing-state-visible enable-2026q1-formatting-improvements ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c715347843="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c715347843="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c715347843="" _nghost-ng-c411533729="" id="message-content-id-r_32ca9b4d3928442d" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c411533729="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color" id="model-response-message-contentr_32ca9b4d3928442d" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-108 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="code-block ng-tns-c3933017335-108 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_32ca9b4d3928442d&quot;,&quot;c_bacbcc7396081285&quot;,null,&quot;rc_878d1af358ab3a64&quot;,null,null,&quot;&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahgKEwiD7sa47-qTAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQwwE" style="display: block;"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c3933017335-108"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c3933017335-108"><!----><pre _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-108"><code _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c3933017335-108 no-decoration-radius">
**Kya aap chahte hain ke main aapko ek video-style screen-by-screenMain aapke liye isay itna asaan bana raha hoon ke agar aapko coding nahi bhi aati, tab bhi aap isay setup kar lenge. Hum isay **"EliteMedBilling-Fullstack"** folder ke naam se banayenge.

Neeche diye gaye steps ko follow karein. Main saara code blocks mein de raha hoon.

---

### **Step 1: Apne Computer Par Folder Banayein**
Apne computer (Desktop) par ek naya folder banayein jiska naam rakhein: `elitemed-billing`. Is folder ke andar mazeed 2 folders banayein:
1.  `frontend` (Ismein website ka chehra hoga).
2.  `backend` (Ismein database aur admin logic hoga).

---

### **Step 2: Backend Setup (The Engine)**
`backend` folder ke andar ek file banayein `server.js` aur ye code paste karein:
```javascript
// backend/server.js
const express = require('express');
const mongoose = require('mongoose');
const cors = require('cors');
require('dotenv').config();

const app = express();
app.use(cors());
app.use(express.json());

// Database Connection
mongoose.connect(process.env.MONGODB_URI)
  .then(() =&gt; console.log("EliteMed Database Connected"))
  .catch(err =&gt; console.log(err));

// Blog Schema
const PostSchema = new mongoose.Schema({
  title: String,
  content: String,
  image: String,
  createdAt: { type: Date, default: Date.now }
});
const Post = mongoose.model('Post', PostSchema);

// API Routes
app.get('/api/posts', async (req, res) =&gt; {
  const posts = await Post.find().sort({ createdAt: -1 });
  res.json(posts);
});

app.post('/api/posts', async (req, res) =&gt; {
  const newPost = new Post(req.body);
  await newPost.save();
  res.json({ message: "Post Created Successfully!" });
});

const PORT = process.env.PORT || 5000;
app.listen(PORT, () =&gt; console.log(`Server running on port ${PORT}`));
</code></pre><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><hr data-path-to-node="1"><h3 data-path-to-node="2"><b data-path-to-node="2" data-index-in-node="0">Step 3: Frontend Setup (The Website)</b></h3><p data-path-to-node="3"><code data-path-to-node="3" data-index-in-node="0">frontend</code> folder ke andar ek file banayein <code data-path-to-node="3" data-index-in-node="42">page.js</code> (Next.js format) aur ye code paste karein. Ismein humne aapka logo aur premium blue theme rakha hai.</p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-109 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="code-block ng-tns-c3933017335-109 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_32ca9b4d3928442d&quot;,&quot;c_bacbcc7396081285&quot;,null,&quot;rc_878d1af358ab3a64&quot;,null,null,&quot;&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahgKEwiD7sa47-qTAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQxAE" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c3933017335-109 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-109">JavaScript</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="buttons ng-tns-c3933017335-109 