----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element> par jayein aur naya "Repository" banayein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="8,0,1,1,0">Apne <code data-path-to-node="8,0,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="5">elitemed-billing</code> folder ki files ko wahan <b data-path-to-node="8,0,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="47">Drag and Drop</b> kar dein.</p></li></ul></li><li><p data-path-to-node="8,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="8,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Cloudflare Pages Connect:</b></p><ul data-path-to-node="8,1,1"><li><p data-path-to-node="8,1,1,0,0">Cloudflare dashboard mein jayein -&gt; <b data-path-to-node="8,1,1,0,0" data-index-in-node="36">Workers &amp; Pages</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="8,1,1,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="8,1,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Create Application</b> -&gt; <b data-path-to-node="8,1,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="22">Pages</b> -&gt; <b data-path-to-node="8,1,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="31">Connect to Git</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="8,1,1,2,0">Apna GitHub account link karein aur <code data-path-to-node="8,1,1,2,0" data-index-in-node="36">elitemed-billing</code> repository select karein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="8,1,1,3,0"><b data-path-to-node="8,1,1,3,0" data-index-in-node="0">Save and Deploy</b> par click karein. Aapki website 2 minute mein live ho jayegi.</p></li></ul></li><li><p data-path-to-node="8,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="8,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Domain Connection:</b></p><ul data-path-to-node="8,2,1"><li><p data-path-to-node="8,2,1,0,0">Jab website live ho jaye, Cloudflare mein "Custom Domains" par jayein aur apna domain (e.g. elitemedbilling.com) likh dein.</p></li></ul></li></ol><hr data-path-to-node="9"><h3 data-path-to-node="10"><b data-path-to-node="10" data-index-in-node="0">Step 5: Edit Kaise Karein?</b></h3><ul data-path-to-node="11"><li><p data-path-to-node="11,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="11,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Logo Change:</b> Apna naya logo <code data-path-to-node="11,0,0" data-index-in-node="28">frontend/public</code> folder mein <code data-path-to-node="11,0,0" data-index-in-node="56">logo.png</code> ke naam se save karein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="11,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="11,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Blog Post:</b> Admin panel (jo humne <code data-path-to-node="11,1,0" data-index-in-node="33">backend</code> mein banaya) par ja kar aap Title aur Content likhenge to wo website par "Blog" section mein show hoga.</p></li></ul><p data-path-to-node="12"><b data-path-to-node="12" data-index-in-node="0">Note:</b> Main aapko ek <b data-path-to-node="12" data-index-in-node="20"><code data-path-to-node="12" data-index-in-node="20">.env</code></b> file ka format bhi de raha hoon, ye aapne zaroor banana hai (Secret Key):</p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-110 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="code-block ng-tns-c3933017335-110 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_32ca9b4d3928442d&quot;,&quot;c_bacbcc7396081285&quot;,null,&quot;rc_878d1af358ab3a64&quot;,null,null,&quot;&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahgKEwiD7sa47-qTAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQxgE" style="display: block;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c3933017335-110 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-110">Plaintext</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="buttons ng-tns-c3933017335-110 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" aria-label="Download code" mat-icon-button=""