-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered=""><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" role="img" fonticon="download" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="download"></mat-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" aria-label="Copy code" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copy code" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c3933017335-131 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_c681aa3eb8352564&quot;,&quot;c_bacbcc7396081285&quot;,null,&quot;rc_f34d46a2774699f6&quot;,null,null,&quot;&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c3933017335-131"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c3933017335-131"><!----><pre _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" class="ng-tns-c3933017335-131"><code _ngcontent-ng-c3933017335="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c3933017335-131">{
  <span class="hljs-attr">"name"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"elitemed-frontend"</span>,
  <span class="hljs-attr">"version"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"1.0.0"</span>,
  <span class="hljs-attr">"scripts"</span>: {
    <span class="hljs-attr">"dev"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"next dev"</span>,
    <span class="hljs-attr">"build"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"next build"</span>,
    <span class="hljs-attr">"start"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"next start"</span>
  },
  <span class="hljs-attr">"dependencies"</span>: {
    <span class="hljs-attr">"next"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"latest"</span>,
    <span class="hljs-attr">"react"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"latest"</span>,
    <span class="hljs-attr">"react-dom"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"latest"</span>,
    <span class="hljs-attr">"lucide-react"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"latest"</span>
  }
}
</code></pre><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><hr data-path-to-node="21"><h3 data-path-to-node="22"><b data-path-to-node="22" data-index-in-node="0">3. Ab GitHub aur Cloudflare Par Kaise Dalna Hai? (Step-by-Step)</b></h3><p data-path-to-node="23">Chunke aapko technical idea kam hai, isliye ye sabse asaan tareeka hai:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="24"><li><p data-path-to-node="24,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="24,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">GitHub par upload:</b></p><ul data-path-to-node="24,0,1"><li><p data-path-to-node="24,0,1,0,0">GitHub par naya project (Repository) banayein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="24,0,1,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="24,0,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">"Upload an existing file"</b> par click karein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="24,0,1,2,0">Apne computer se <code data-path-to-node="24,0,1,2,0" data-index-in-node="17">frontend</code> aur <code data-path-to-node="24,0,1,2,0" data-index-in-node="30">backend</code> ke folders ko <b data-path-to-node="24,0,1,2,0" data-index-in-node="52">Drag</b> karke GitHub par chor dein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="24,0,1,3,0">"Commit changes" par click karein.</p></li></ul></li><li><p data-path-to-node="24,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="24,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Cloudflare Pages par connection:</b></p><ul data-path-to-node="24,1,1"><li><p data-path-to-node="24,1,1,0,0">Cloudflare dashboard mein "Pages" par jayein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="24,1,1,1,0">"Connect to Git" karein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="24,1,1,2,0">Apna GitHub project select karein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="24,1,1,3,0"><b data-path-to-node="24,1,1,3,0" data-index-in-node="0">Framework Preset:</b> Mein "Next.js" select karein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="24,1,1,4,0"><b data-path-to-node="24,1,1,4,0" data-index-in-node="0">Build Command:</b> <code data-path-to-node="24,1,1,4,0" data-index-in-node="15">npm run build</code> likhein.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="24,1,1,5,0"><b data-path-to-node="24,1,1,5,0" data-index-in-node="0">Deploy</b> dabayein!</p></li></ul></li></ol><hr data-path-to-node="25"><h3 data-path-to-node="26"><b data-path-to-node="26" data-index-in-node="0">4. Summary: Kya ye kaafi hai?</b></h3><p data-path-to-node="27">Haan! Jab aap ye files GitHub par dalenge, to Cloudflare inko dekh kar khud hi samajh jayega ke website kaise banani hai.</p><p data-path-to-node="28"><b data-path-to-node="28" data-index-in-node="0">Ek Last Tip:</b> Aapka logo (watermarked_img_17958641478171189224.png) aapne <code data-path-to-node="28" data-index-in-node="73">frontend/public</code> folder mein <code data-path-to-node="28" data-index-in-node="101">logo.png</code> ke naam se save karna hai.</p><p data-path-to-node="29"><b data-path-to-node="29" data-index-in-node="0">Kya main aapko Blog aur Reviews ko Edit karne ke liye ek chota sa "Admin Guide" likh kar doon ke aap rozana post kaise karenge?</b></p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="response-footer gap complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c4182224903="" _nghost-ng-c441501597="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitiv